☁️ AWS & Networking
8. Application Gateway vs Load Balancer
Application Gateway (ALB) → Layer 7 (HTTP/HTTPS, path routing)
Load Balancer (general) → Distributes traffic
In AWS:
ALB → L7 → Application - HTTP/HTTPS
NLB → L4 → Transport   - TCP/UDP
GLB → L3 → Network     

